1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:58,719
Look.

4
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:00,719
He looks just like

5
00:01:00,719 --> 00:01:01,439
you.

6
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,479
He's so adorable.

7
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:05,959
You must teach him yourself
when he grows up.

8
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:07,120
Yes.

9
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:09,359
I will teach him

10
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:10,599
calligraphy,

11
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:11,599
poetry,

12
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,439
horseback riding,

13
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,159
and hunting.

14
00:01:13,159 --> 00:01:13,760
How about that?

15
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,359
Great.

16
00:01:16,359 --> 00:01:17,120
Your Majesty.

17
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,079
Your Majesty.

18
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:18,920
Your Majesty.

19
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:19,879
Something terrible has happened.

20
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:21,840
Lord of Zhenbei has stormed
the city with his men.

21
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,920
Lord of Zhenbei?

22
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,280
What about the city guards?

23
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,959
How could they not stop him?

24
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:27,719
Reporting, Your Majesty.

25
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:29,159
The guards at the gate said

26
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:31,079
someone showed the imperial decree
outside the city at nightfall.

27
00:01:31,079 --> 00:01:31,799
It was too dark

28
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,680
to see the person's face.

29
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:34,400
They claimed
it was Your Majesty's order,

30
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,519
so the guards

31
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:36,799
opened the gate without delay.

32
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:37,599
Upon closer look,

33
00:01:37,599 --> 00:01:39,079
it was the Holy Maiden.

34
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:39,920
Just as the guards

35
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,319
were about to seize her,

36
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:43,200
the rebel forces waiting outside

37
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,799
attacked and broke through.

38
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:46,040
The guards were caught off guard

39
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,159
and were forced to retreat.

40
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,640
The rebels are about to break in.

41
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,400
Please, Your Majesty,
take cover immediately.

42
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,439
Jiang Yukui.

43
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,879
I should never have spared you.

44
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,239
Zhaohua.

45
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,920
Hide here with our son.

46
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,439
I...

47
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:35,800
Lord of Zhenbei.

48
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,479
How dare you rebel?

49
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,439
You're a tyrant.

50
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,000
You've brought ruin to the kingdom.

51
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,599
Everyone has the right to kill you.

52
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:44,639
I am merely following the will of Heaven

53
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,919
and taking your place.

54
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:50,599
Zhaohua.

55
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,479
The tyrant deserves to die,

56
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,319
but you are his subject.

57
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:55,560
Plotting rebellion,

58
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,919
betraying your ruler,

59
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,719
that makes you even more deserving
of death.

60
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:01,520
I've been waiting for you.

61
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,879
You knew I would come today?

62
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:49,680
My Lord.

63
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,680
Where is Yukui?

64
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,520
I haven't seen her.

65
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,120
But

66
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,599
our horses are gone.

67
00:04:29,079 --> 00:04:30,000
Zhaohua.

68
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,800
You saved me.

69
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,759
Your Majesty.

70
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,920
Does it hurt?

71
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,800
Zhaohua.

72
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,560
With you by my side,

73
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,519
I feel no pain at all.

74
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,040
Zhaohua.

75
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,480
Your Zhaohua

76
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,399
died long ago.

77
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,120
You don't recognize me anymore?

78
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:02,319
I'm Yusang.

79
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,399
(Why do you also have the Divine Power?)

80
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,040
(You must be wondering)

81
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,000
(why you can never hurt me.)

82
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,920
(What is happening?)

83
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:01,759
(What?)

84
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,160
(The Divine Power)

85
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,079
(isn't working?)

86
00:06:06,079 --> 00:06:08,360
(Do you think I can't kill you
right now?)

87
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,759
(My Divine Power,)

88
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:20,120
(why isn't it working?)

89
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:48,199
(When camellias bloom,)

90
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,959
(twin shadows appear.)

91
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:51,439
(One flower, one life,)

92
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:53,040
(bound together.)

93
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:55,000
(With this blood mark,)

94
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,360
(even if we are miles apart,)

95
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,519
(we will still)

96
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,040
(feel each other,)

97
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,279
(until one of us dies.)

98
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,120
(Kui.)

99
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:19,160
(Don't you recognize your sister?)

100
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,920
(Sister.)

101
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,959
(Sister.)

102
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,920
(Sister, you're alive?)

103
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,399
(But)

104
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,879
(how do you have Consort Rong's face?)

105
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,040
(Why is this happening?)

106
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:42,920
(Aren't you...)

107
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,319
(In your eyes,)

108
00:07:49,319 --> 00:07:50,639
(I couldn't even handle)

109
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:52,600
(someone as ordinary)

110
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,480
(as Rong Zhaohua?)

111
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:00,959
(Jiang Yusang.)

112
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,879
(Why did you deceive me?)

113
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,759
(Why?)

114
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,199
(Your Majesty.)

115
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,600
(Trust me.)

116
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,120
(I would never harm you.)

117
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:14,399
(This poison has nothing to do with me.)

118
00:08:14,399 --> 00:08:15,680
(The evidence is clear.)

119
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,800
(What more can you say?)

120
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:21,519
(Someone is framing me.)

121
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,480
(Gu worms
originate from the Zhao Tribe.)

122
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,639
(Who else could have done this?)

123
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:31,040
(Now Kun wants to
absorb the Zhao Tribe,)

124
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,759
(so you resent His Majesty for it.)

125
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,240
(If not you, then who?)

126
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,240
(That's not true.)

127
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:38,759
(I came for the alliance willingly.)

128
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,440
(I wanted to use myself)

129
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,960
(to keep peace between our two nations.)

130
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,080
(Your Majesty.)

131
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,480
(She admitted it.)

132
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:46,519
(She had ulterior motives
for the alliance.)

133
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,559
(Of course,)

134
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,840
(for the Zhao Tribe,)

135
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,960
(the fall of Kun)

136
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,360
(would be safer.)

137
00:08:52,639 --> 00:08:53,399
(That's not true.)

138
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:54,200
(Your Majesty.)

139
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,200
(At first, I came for the alliance)

140
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,639
(to keep our nations at peace.)

141
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,600
(But as I spent time with you,)

142
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:06,440
(my feelings became real.)

143
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,440
(Your Majesty,)

144
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:10,240
(everything I felt was real.)

145
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,039
(Real?)

146
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,360
(Don't try to deceive him.)

147
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,240
(Tell me.)

148
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,559
(Who could love the man)

149
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:21,200
(who tore her from her lover?)

150
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,240
(Bring him in.)

151
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:30,879
(Your Majesty.)

152
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:33,720
(This man is called Li.)

153
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,440
(He often acts suspiciously)

154
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,600
(near Kun's border.)

155
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,519
(I suspected)

156
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:40,320
(he was a spy from a foreign tribe,)

157
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,759
(so I captured him.)

158
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,399
(After questioning him,)

159
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:46,000
(it turns out he's not a spy.)

160
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,480
(He came to see)

161
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,679
(his beloved in the Zhao Tribe,)

162
00:09:49,679 --> 00:09:51,639
(the Holy Maiden Jiang Yusang.)

163
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:01,320
(Zhu Yunqi was cruel,)

164
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:03,799
(but worse than that,
he was suspicious by nature.)

165
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,639
(Since I entered the palace,)

166
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:08,399
(I focused on gaining his trust)

167
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:10,639
(and controlling his mind)

168
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:12,080
(to rule the realm.)

169
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:14,919
(But I overlooked one thing,
a man's heart.)

170
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,639
(A man's heart?)

171
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:17,879
(Since ancient times,)

172
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:20,000
(people have said women are jealous)

173
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,919
(and fight for a man's affection.)

174
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,279
(But a man's jealousy)

175
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,639
(can be even worse)

176
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:26,639
(than a woman's.)

177
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,120
(In their eyes,)

178
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:29,080
(women are nothing more)

179
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,440
(than possessions,)

180
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,159
(untouchable by anyone else.)

181
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:34,600
(Rong Zhaohua understood this
better than I did.)

182
00:10:36,159 --> 00:10:37,559
(It was my own carelessness.)

183
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,720
(I never guarded against her,)

184
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:42,039
(and I gave her an opening.)

185
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:42,759
(Then,)

186
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:45,120
(how did you become Rong Zhaohua?)

187
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:49,279
(I have her arrogance to thank.)

188
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:51,360
(She insisted on handling me privately,)

189
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,399
(which gave me the perfect chance.)

190
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,559
(You dare compete with me
for His Majesty's favor?)

191
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,279
(All these torture devices)

192
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:07,600
(are prepared for you.)

193
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,240
(Today, you will taste)

194
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:14,080
(my power.)

195
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,039
(I never wanted to compete with you.)

196
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:24,360
(I don't want to hear it.)

197
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,200
(What's happening?)

198
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:03,440
(Why can't I control)

199
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,480
(my own body?)

200
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:07,279
(Jiang Yusang.)

201
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:08,799
(Let me go.)

202
00:12:12,919 --> 00:12:14,720
(Your mind is consumed)

203
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,600
(with schemes)

204
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,519
(and the Emperor's favor.)

205
00:12:20,519 --> 00:12:23,279
(You naturally assumed he married me)

206
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:25,679
(for my looks.)

207
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:29,080
(He summoned me night after night)

208
00:12:30,159 --> 00:12:32,399
(so I could use the Divine Power)

209
00:12:32,399 --> 00:12:33,960
(to peer into people's hearts.)

210
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,000
(The Divine Power?)

211
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,960
(You truly know nothing about it.)

212
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:45,399
(It seems
His Majesty never trusted you.)

213
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:47,960
(You were nothing but a plaything.)

214
00:12:48,039 --> 00:12:49,000
(You liar!)

215
00:12:49,399 --> 00:12:51,519
(His Majesty truly loves me.)

216
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,559
(How could he see me
as a mere plaything?)

217
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,679
(You're jealous of me.)

218
00:12:55,679 --> 00:12:57,519
(All of you are jealous of me.)

219
00:12:57,519 --> 00:12:59,240
(Thanks to you,)

220
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,159
(when my Divine Power)

221
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:03,360
(was sealed within the Mirror Prison,)

222
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:05,759
(it was that hatred)

223
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:10,000
(that broke through my shackles.)

224
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,919
(On the brink of death,)

225
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:15,480
(it was tempered again and again
between light and shadow,)

226
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,559
(allowing the Divine Power)

227
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:18,919
(to grow even stronger.)

228
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:15,100
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

229
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:17,020
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

230
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:20,340
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

231
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:24,460
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

232
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:29,140
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

233
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,660
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

234
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:34,420
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

235
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:38,420
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

236
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:42,740
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

237
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:46,300
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

238
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:48,620
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

239
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:52,820
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

240
00:14:53,260 --> 00:14:54,900
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

241
00:14:54,900 --> 00:14:56,420
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

242
00:14:56,420 --> 00:14:59,620
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

243
00:15:00,020 --> 00:15:01,940
♪In dreams, it's you♪

244
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:03,340
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

245
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:06,660
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

246
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:10,060
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

247
00:15:10,060 --> 00:15:13,620
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

248
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:16,860
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

249
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:20,300
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
